	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sounds like its great when you're quad kiting and out of mana to shackle. This baby will also save mana when recasting on already snared mobs that are already grouped by you.<br><br>The reason they make weapons like this for casters is because casters are capped at 110 weapon skill, and will cause no balance issues when they melee with something like this.<br><br>Reason they don't make an item like this for a rogue is the same reason they don't put the backstab ability on a dagger for casters.<br><br>Most items that are clickable have effects that the class can already produce. Very rare do you see an item that has an ability from another class. There are a few, but they are sort of balanced.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
